Privacy Policy

Effective Date: March 28,2024

NYC Weather ("we", "us", or "our") operates the NYC Weather mobile application (the "Service").

This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.

Information We Collect

While using our Service, we may collect certain information that could be used to identify you ("Personal Data").

Non-Personal Data: We may also collect non-personally identifiable information ("Non-Personal Data") that does not directly identify an individual user.
This data may include usage data such as location data (city level, not precise GPS coordinates) to display relevant weather information.
We may use cookies and other tracking technologies to collect and store Non-Personal Data.
Use of Data

NYC Weather uses the collected data for various purposes:

To provide and maintain the Service
To improve the Service
To personalize the user experience
To analyze how the Service is used
To prevent or detect technical problems
Disclosure of Data

We may disclose your Personal Data under certain circumstances:

To service providers we employ to operate and maintain the Service
To comply with legal obligations
To protect the rights and safety of users
Data Retention

We will retain your Personal Data only for as long as necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy.

Security

The security of your data is important to us. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Children's Privacy

Our Service does not address anyone under the age of [Age Limit, e.g., 13]. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has used our Service, please contact us. If we become aware that we have collected Personal Data from a child under 13, we will take steps to remove that information from our servers.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: nycweatherapp@qompu.com
